description.narrative: This activity (Business Innovation Facility Phase 2) is a component of Business Innovation Facility (BIF) reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £22,923,640. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Business Policy and Administration. , with the following implementing partners: PwC. The start date is 03-09-2014 and the end date is 31-12-2019.
